=== 体育 ===
邓迪市共有两支职业足球俱乐部，[[邓迪足球俱乐部|邓迪足球俱乐部]]和[[邓迪联足球俱乐部|邓迪联足球俱乐部]]，它们是传统的敌对球队。两队的主场在同一条大街，相距仅200码（183米），是英国境内相距最近的两个职业足球俱乐部主场球场。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.football-stadiums.co.uk/grounds/scotland/tannadice-park/|title=Tannadice Park Dundee United|access-date=2018-08-12|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124191142/https://www.football-stadiums.co.uk/grounds/scotland/tannadice-park/|dead-url=no}}</ref>中国球星[[范志毅|范志毅]]曾于2001-2002年间在邓迪联队效力。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee/2238683.stm|title=Fan deserts Dundee|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] News|date=2002-09-05|access-date=2018-08-12|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004034540/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee/2238683.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
