== 教育 ==
邓迪市有两所大学：[[邓迪大学|邓迪大学]]和[[亚伯泰大学|亚伯泰大学]]。除此之外，还有一所[[继续教育|继续教育]]学院和一所教师培训学校。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dundeecity.gov.uk/service-area/city-development/planning-and-economic-development/dundee-one-city-many-discoveries|title=''DUNDEE One City, Many Discoveries''|publisher=Dundee City Council|access-date=2018-08-07|archive-date=2019-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513032640/https://www.dundeecity.gov.uk/service-area/city-development/planning-and-economic-development/dundee-one-city-many-discoveries|dead-url=no}}</ref>

亚伯泰大学的前身是1988年成立的邓迪理工学院。

